cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DM, cs.NE, cs.SI 

The paper proposes a novel evolving ensemble classifier for data streams, which involves machine learning techniques such as ensemble learning, online feature selection, and drift detection. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DM (Data Mining). The paper also involves neural networks, which makes cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) a possible category. Finally, the paper deals with complex environments, which could make cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) a relevant category.
